<CL>
M7 chai-iaN2 tak8-e5 kam2 u7 chit-e5 kam2-kak, to7 si7 chng-kha-lang5 chiok heng3 ngia5-lau7-jiat8--e5; chhiuN7 goan2 chng 3-ni5 1-kai3 e5 “gia5-ong5”, to7 si7 goan2 put-chi2-a2 ki5-thai7 e5 jit8-chi2.
2000-ni5 Lan2-lang5 3-goeh8 17, si7 goan2 chng e5 “gia5-ong5”. Chit-kang si7 pai3-5, goa2 tu2-a2-ho2 bo5 kho3, pai3-4 e-pou to7 khok8 hoe2-chhia tng2 Pin5-tong, kau3 chhu3--nih ma7 am3-si5 10-tiam2--a.
Tng2-khi3 chhu3 e5 lou7--nih kap a-pa3 bong2-oe7, i kong2 eng3-kai ai3 kong2 “ngia5-ong5”, to7 si7 ngia5 ong5-ia5 e5 i3-su3. Chit-ma2 chng--nih e5 lang5 long2 kong2 “gia5-ong5”, goa2 siuN7, eng3-kai si7 chau2-im iah si7 kan2-hoa3 e5 koan-he7.
A-pa3 koh kong2, ong5-ia5 si7 Giok8-hong5-tai7-te3 phai3 lai5 hoan5-kan sun5-si7--e5, chit-kho si7 Chhi5-hu2-ong5-ia5, tak8-kho e5 ong5-ia5 long2 bo5 kang5, chhiaN2-sin5 e5 te7-tiam2 ma7 bo5 kou3-teng7. Chit-kai3 tu2-a2-ho2 3-chng kang7 1-kang gia5-ong5---- goan2-chng PheN5-chhu3 kap keh-piah-chng Sin-chng-a2, Su7-iong5.
An2-ne kong2--khi2-lai5, m7 to7 ai3 u7 chiok che7 ong5-ia5, bo5 nah u7 hoat-tou7 eng3-hu3 chiah-ni7 che7 chng e5 gia5-ong5? Beh nah e7 u7 hiah-ni7 che7 ong5-ia5--leh? Kam2 kong2 goa2 si2 liau2-au7 ma7 e7 hong5 chio-khi3 cho3 ong5-ia5?
3-goeh8 17 chit-kang, thau3-cha2 2-tiam2 to7 ai3 khi3 chhiaN2-sin5, kian3-pai2 chhiaN2-sin5 e5 te7-tiam2 long2 ti7 khe-a2-piN, goa2 ma7 m7 chai-iaN2 si7 an2-choaN2? Chit-kai3 si7 ti7 Li2-kang2 1-keng soa-chioh8-a2-tiuN5 lai7-te2 e5 khe-a2.
Goa2 chit-e5 toe3-som5--e5, kui-me5 bo5 khun3, au kau3 tiam2-poaN3 to7 che7 be7-tiau5--a. Chit-chun7, goa7-khau2 i2-keng u7 lang5 tih tin2-tang7, ma7 thiaN-tioh8 bio7-kong tih hong3-sang3, chhui tak8-e5 kin2 lai5 bio7-tiaN5 chun2-pi7.
KiaN5 kau3 bio7-tiaN5, oah! Chiok che7 lang5 long2 chhut--lai5-a, tin7-thau5 ma7 chun2-pi7 kah chha-put-to--a, 6-teng2 ong5-kio7 chhai7 ti7 hia, 1-koa2 lang5 tih khoan2 phau3 kap ian-hoe2, chiok lau7-jiat8--e5.
ChhiaN2-sin5 e5 koe3-teng5 it-tit8 kau3 chai2-khi2 8-tiam2-poaN3 chiah sng3 kiat-sok.
Gia5-ong5 chit-kang, tak8-hou7 tiong-tau3 kap am3-si5 long2 e7 pan7-toh chhiaN2 chhin-chiaN5 peng5-iu2, che si7 goan2 chia--e5 gin2-a2 siong7 heng3--e5.
Hioh-tau3 soah, e-pou 2-tiam2-poaN3 khai-si2 un5-keng2, to7 si7 un5-chng e5 i3-su3.
Chhoa7-thau5--e5 si7 khai-lou7-kou2, koh lai5 si7 tin7-thau5, chit-kho kan-taN chhun leng5-tin7, song3-kang-tin7 kap 2-e5 toa7-kou2-tin7, bo5 tah8-khiau kap sai2-le5-a2--a.
Tin7-thau5 au7-piah to7 si7 ong5-kio7, tang5-ki khia7 ti7 kio7 teng2-koan5, tin7-thau5 e7 ti7 tak8-hou7 mng5-khau2 bu2-lang7, chit-chun7, lang5 e7 chun2-pi7 ang5-pau hou7--in, sng3 si7 kou2-le7 kap kam2-sia7 e5 sim-i3. Ong5-kio7 to7 bo5 tek-khak e7 theng5--loh8-lai5, m7-koh Gou7-goan5-soe3 u7 jip8-lai5 goan2-tau oe7 hu5-a2, kam2 si7 u7 chai-ek?
It-tit8 kau3 5-tiam2-goa7 chiah un5 liau2 beh jip8-bio7, jip8-bio7 si7 kui-e5 gia5-ong5 siong7-jiat8 e5 si5-chun7. Sui-bong2 tin7-thau5 lu2 lai5 lu2 chio2, m7-koh iah si7 kang7-khoan2 lau7-jiat8, chhut-goa7 phah-piaN3 e5 lang5 long2 e7 tng2--lai5, peng5-siong5-si5-a2 han2 tih khoaN3--tioh8-e5, chit-chun7 ma7 long2 chau2--chhut-lai5-a.
Chng-kha-lang5 bo5 siaN2-mih eng5-chiN5, m7-koh goan2 hia tak8-kho gia5-ong5 long2 u7 khoan2 chiok che7 phau3 kap ian-hoe2--e5, kian3-pai2 na7 khoaN3-tioh8 phau3-a2 tih pang3, to7 ka2-na2 khoaN3-tioh8 chiN5 1-pe2 1-pe2 tih ia7--leh.
Goan2 chit-keng bio7 pai3--e5 si7 Chia7-hu2-goan5-soe3, thiaN-kong2 in u7 5-e5 hiaN-ti7-a2, kan-taN SaN-goan5-soe3 kap Gou7-goan5-soe3 u7 tang5-ki. Goan2 a-pa3 to7 si7 saN-goan5-soe3 e5 tang5-ki, chu7 se3-han3 goa2 to7 tui3 tang5-ki chiok houN3-hian5--e5, m7-koh long2 m7-kaN2 mng7--i.
Goa2 thak8 kok-tiong e5 si5, u7 1-kai3 ka2-na2 mng7 i kong2, khi2-tang5 tih chhau kam2 e7 thiaN3 iah si7 u7 siaN2-mih kam2-kak chit-khoan2 bun7-te5, i sui7 soa2 tui3 pat8-e5 oe7-te5 khi3, bo5 in3--goa2. Chu7 hit-chun7 khai-si2, goa2 to7 koh khah bo5 iong2-khi3 mng7 i che--a.
Chit-kai3 khi3 chhiaN2-sin5, ti7 hia tih chhiaN2 goan5-soe3 loh8--lai5, beh ngia5 ong5-ia5 chiuN7-hoaN7 e5 si5-chun7, soah chhiaN2 long2 bo5, tak8-e5 ti7 hia tan2 kui-pou-ku2, goa2 to7 chau2 khi3 goan2 a-pa3 piN-a2, mng7 i hoat-seng siaN2-mih tai7-chi3, i kan-taN kong2 ai3 tan2--1-e7, goa2 to7 koh chau2 tui3 pat8-giah khi3. Koe3 bo5 joa7 ku2, i to7 khi2-tang5--a.
Boe2--a2, siuN7 siuN7--leh, ka-ti7 sit8-chai7 chiok peh8-lan7--e5, hit-chun7 khoaN3 i ka-ti7 khia7 ti7 hia, eng3-kai to7 chai-iaN2 i u7 kam2-eng3--a, goa2 koh peh8-chhi peh8-chhi chau2 khi3 mng7 i hoat-seng siaN2-mih tai7-chi3.
Chit-ma2, goan2 chng--nih e5 toa7-tai7-chi3 to7 kan-taN chhun gia5-ong5 kap 5-goeh8 chhe-5 sin5-beng5 seN-jit8, chia--e5 oah8-tang7 si7 lian5-lok8 kap i5-chhi5 chhoan-bin5 cheng5-kam2 e5 chu2-iau3 lek8-liong7. Chin-ka-chai3, chng-a2-lang5 koh chiok tiong7-si7 gia5-ong5--e5, bo5 hou7 i bo5--khi3, na7 bo5, goan2 chit-chng cha2 to7 pang--khi3-a.
Chit-kai3 gia5-ong5 hoat-seng chiaN5 che7 chhio3-khoe-tai7, ma7 u7 1-koa2 i3-goa7. Tan2 3-ni5, an2-ne 1-kang to7 koe3--khi3-a, chiok be7 koe3-gian3--e5, aih.... koh ai3 tan2 3-ni5 chiah e7-sai2 koh kam2-siu7-tioh8 gia5-ong5 e5 un-loan2.
(TGB Thong-sin3 te7 9 ki5, 2000 ni5 6 goeh8)
</CL>
